@sxjscience 
Add `mx.nd.waitall()` after `choose_element_0index` will solve this problem.
But will also decrease the speed.

@liuxialong Could you help submit an example code that reproduces this error message?
Also, what's your CUDA version and GPU version? Random generator in CUDA 7.5 does not work on Pascal GPUs.
See also https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/issues/1240
